Name: TypeOfEvaluation
Description: Brief identification of the type of evaluation. Supports the use of an external controlled vocabulary.

Name: Evaluator
Description: Identifies the evaluator and specifies the role of the evaluator using an external controlled vocabulary.

Name: EvaluationProcess
Description: Describes the evaluation process. Supports multi-lingual content. Allows the optional use of structured content.

Name: Outcomes
Description: Describes the outcomes of the evaluation process. Supports multi-lingual content. Allows the optional use of structured content.

Name: CompletionDate
Description: Identifies the date the evaluation was completed.
